channel.title: How to get my server up and running
channel.description: How do i get my server up and running, i got a no-ip account with a host (ddsbltz.no-ip.biz) and i got a source downloaded and extracted on my comp (ddsspeced) and im on a lab top with a linkus router if that has anything to do with it... so i click run server and this black box comes up and says server is online!!! but when i ty to log into it it says server is off line, the little no-ip download box dat makes da face is with the two red dots on his cheek, help me!!! (my first runescape p server and im exited to get it up and running :D)
